**** This is the menu ***
SELECT TABLE OR EXECUTE SQL:
   Example of usage:
	> assignments
	(switches mode from 'sql' to 'assignments' and displays table)
	(from now on, any operation done now should relate to assignments)
	(unless mode is switched back to 'sql')

	> select <id>
	(display one row)

	> insert
	(launch insert wizard/form/questionary, update db, update view)

	> update <id>
	(launches update menu, update db, update view)

	> delete <id>
	(update db, update view)

	> add more commands au besoin
